docs.text: Indonesia Island ¶ Indonesian Island is a Roblox game where you can meet other people and play with your friends. Indonesia Island was founded by Keeolyx on 14/12/2021 and managed by Rehan Productions™ I XQII46 as a developer who is always updating the game to make it more interesting for everyone. Now there are more than 500+ people who have tried to play Indonesian Island with their friends! Come play now with your friends! or do you want to try the developer version? Of course you can! Try it! or Learn more about developer version. Did you find a bug or did someone cheat? Come report it on our Discord server and go to #support-ticket or press feedback (On TopBar UI) button in the game or you can DM Vyx#4921 Developers ¶ zenmathofans02 XQII46 Keeolyx
